Window Methods

open()
    • opens a new window

close()
    • closes the current window

moveTo()
    • move the current window

resizeTo()
    • resize the current window

alert()
    • displays the alert box containing message with ok button.

confirm ()
    • displays the confirm dialog box containing message with ok and cancel button.

prompt()
    • displays a dialog box to get input from the user.

setTimeout()
    • performs action after specified time like calling function, evaluating expressions


history.back()
history.forward()


